2. Choose Inpateint in Dimensions

2. Choose Impatient in Dimensions:

Create Parameter called inpatient Dynamic Dimensions. right click on create Parameter. select list in parameter option. in value write DRG Definition and Display as Bar Graph. Hospital Referral region and Display as Line Graph. Provider State and Display as Tree Graph.then click ok. 

Create Calculated Field “Choose Inpatients Details”.  go to analysis and click on create calculated field. write these below script and then click ok

CASE [Inpatient Dynamic Dimensions]
WHEN 'Provider City' THEN [Provider City]
WHEN 'Provider Name' THEN [Provider Name]
WHEN 'DRG Definition' THEN [DRG Definition]
END


one more calculated field “Index”:

Create Set “Provider State Set”: right click on set and create set and set page will open. select select from list and click ok. right click on set click show filter.

follow below direction. drag and drop in dimensions and measures.   


Go to show me and choose bubble charts


Choose Inpateints Details:

CASE [Inpatient Dynamic Dimensions]
WHEN 'Provider City' THEN [Provider City]
WHEN 'Provider Name' THEN [Provider Name]
WHEN 'DRG Definition' THEN [DRG Definition]
END
